* {
*   "userId": "CP-009",
*   "leadId": "ld-08751",
*   "scheduleDate": "2025-12-10T12:34:56Z",
*   "notes": "This is a note."
* }
*
* Success Response:
* {
*   "status": true,
*   "message": "Site visit's slot added successfully."
* }
